title: Perfect 2-Story Home! – Park in your 2-car garage! – Great Back Yard!

Price $379,900, 5.625% Fixed/ 6.708% APR, 3.5% Down, FHA 30 Year, OAC from third party lender.', 'Other fees such as taxes, insurance and HOA are not included in the sample monthly payment amount.', 'Prices and rates are subject to change without notice.']
